body_text:
The decision to stay with cuda 9.0 was recommended to us by NVIDIA, as the new drivers to support cuda 9.1 is not available everywhere at the moment.
To run TF with cuda 9.1, you can build from sources, and it will definitely work.
@tfboyd can comment more.

